derek.util

Class ArrayHashMap<K,V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.AbstractMap<K,V>
      • derek.util.ArrayHashMap<K,V>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.Map<K,V>

    public class ArrayHashMap<K,V>
extends java.util.AbstractMap<K,V>
    This class implements a hash-map using only arrays. No linked lists at all. Chanllenging thing is challenging. This also extends AbstractMap and uses generic types, so that its not a complete waste of code.
